<p>
<p>You bought two lottery tickets. The first <em>X</em> has a profit expectation of €0.50 with a standard deviation of €0.25 and the second <em>Y</em> €0.75 profit expectation with €0.32 standard deviation. If you exclude the cost of the lots, what is your expectation value of the total profit and its standard deviation?</p>
</p>]]></text>
